{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Shopify Design Challenge â€“ Exit Sign","content":"<html><head></head><body><p>This week&#x2019;s design challenge was to create a monster-themed exit sign for the new Lounge area at the Shopify office. I managed to win the challenge this week (woo!) &#x1F600; </p>\n<p>Here&#x2019;s my entry:</p>\n<p><a href=\"/static/3bbda6f1302da9b7371ee688043f60ae/bc05e/it_lurks_poster.jpg\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 650px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 151.3245033112583%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n    <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image alignnone size-full wp-image-2266\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"it lurks poster\" title=\"it_lurks_poster\" src=\"/static/3bbda6f1302da9b7371ee688043f60ae/a111b/it_lurks_poster.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/3bbda6f1302da9b7371ee688043f60ae/aca85/it_lurks_poster.jpg 163w,\n/static/3bbda6f1302da9b7371ee688043f60ae/0954f/it_lurks_poster.jpg 325w,\n/static/3bbda6f1302da9b7371ee688043f60ae/a111b/it_lurks_poster.jpg 650w,\n/static/3bbda6f1302da9b7371ee688043f60ae/bc05e/it_lurks_poster.jpg 906w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\">\n  </span></a></p>\n<p>I get to hold on to this badboy for a couple of weeks:</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/shopify-belt.jpeg\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/shopify-belt-1024x1024.jpg\" alt title=\"shopify belt\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-2261\"></a></p>\n<div class=\"sub\">Shopify Design Challenge winner belt</div>\n<p><!--more--></p>\n<p>Below is one of my later sketches. I decided to ditch the nostrils because it made him look too &#x2018;piggish&#x2019;. Wish I had time to play around with shading and more details, maybe I&#x2019;ll do that over the weekend or something.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/poster2.jpeg\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/poster2-1024x787.jpg\" alt=\"sketch for poster\" title=\"sketch for poster\" width=\"1024\" height=\"787\" class=\"size-large wp-image-2258\"></a></p>\n</body></html>"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"shopify-design-challenge-exit-sign"}}